44:54.559 --> 45:00.331 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Why do you think that effort
didn't -- it
was bad enough, but why do you
think it got

45:00.364 --> 45:02.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
as far as it did?

45:02.199 --> 45:06.237 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. SIDDHARTHA MUKHERJEE: Well,
