45:23.821 --> 45:28.492 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And a lot of progressives, not
all, but a
lot of progressives signed on to
it and thought

45:28.526 --> 45:33.264 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that it was really great to
improve the human
race by selective breeding.

45:33.297 --> 45:40.171 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now, what is amazing about is
that that idea
metastasizes to America, to our
shores, and

45:40.204 --> 45:44.108 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
becomes, you know -- that
selective human
breeding becomes selective human
sterilization,

45:44.141 --> 45:45.643 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Carrie Buck, a woman...

45:45.676 --> 45:48.613 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: To whom you
dedicate the book,
along with your grandmother.

45:48.646 --> 45:50.481 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. SIDDHARTHA MUKHERJEE: To
whom I dedicate
the book, along with my
grandmother.

45:50.514 --> 45:55.152 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
