this was
our problem, too. This was not
only their

46:20.878 --> 46:24.649 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
problem. This is something that
arose out
of a very particularly moment in
American

46:24.682 --> 46:26.517 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
history.

46:26.550 --> 46:30.821 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: You write -- you
