46:49.674 --> 46:51.409 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
DR. SIDDHARTHA MUKHERJEE: It is
not that simple.

46:51.442 --> 46:54.845 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's very important to remember
what parts
are simple and not. Otherwise,
we need this

46:54.879 --> 47:00.351 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
