medical boardrooms.
It has to had in a wide public
place as possible.

47:06.757 --> 47:13.864 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But things are more complicated,
because your
genes predict the future, but
not in an absolute

47:13.898 --> 47:19.704 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
