sense. In other
words, there is still a striking
role of chance,

47:19.737 --> 47:25.643 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
a striking role of the
environment. It's chance,
plus genes, plus environments,
and these interactions

47:25.676 --> 47:27.945 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
between them that make you and
me.

47:27.978 --> 47:32.383 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the gene predict a little
bit in some
cases, a lot in other cases. And
we need to

47:32.416 --> 47:37.054 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
figure out what I what. We need
