match where genes are useful and
where genes

47:37.088 --> 47:38.923 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
can be misleading.

47:38.956 --> 47:42.960 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, what -- how
