47:53.137 --> 47:58.743 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There is a vast cosmos yet to be
discovered.
How do genes manage to make, you
know, a human

47:58.776 --> 48:00.544 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
