49:54.124 --> 49:59.396 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
I have a lot of musical
influences, Kanye
West, Pharrell William, Frank
Ocean, Stevie

49:59.430 --> 50:05.102 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Wonder. I listen to Stevie when
