way, can provide
the ear candy for a classic.

50:24.755 --> 50:29.760 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
"Runaway" is one of my favorite
tracks, because
it deals with having to leave
something that

50:29.793 --> 50:37.167 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
you know and chasing your own
